{"tid":1486774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟歸家隊友感安慰","createTime":"2019-08-19T03:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T03:50:38.000Z","uid":239351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2bcd82a7b9a4daa5e26eb7cd5cc3b4cb8a193d9","tid":1486774,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"每個星期日要見到手足受傷，要見到警察濫權，星期一就要睇住一堆令人心痛嘅新聞。<br />\n<br />\n今個星期大家都平安返到屋企 （梁金城除外），難得有一個星期可以算係比勇武嘅休息。講贏，到而家都冇人贏任何野，因為五大訴求都未被答應。<br />\n<br />\n我地<strong>不自滿、不自high</strong>、但要知道<br />\n大家平安返到屋企係一件值得安慰嘅事。"},{"pid":"a219b2f271d132b7c0b82f8553d714c8aee10787","tid":1486774,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d4f32933ced137eadb0c69fc0999fcb6e173542","tid":1486774,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"120cb8442f49fc9ac21b5b5796c75085e977004f","tid":1486774,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:50:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}